  "Description": {
    "English": "An anomalous egg. Since the encounter with the bizarre deep-space 'creature', its strange music has grown more active, more agitated.<br><br>When touched, conjures a powerful vision of a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">dust-covered world</span> of <span class=\"name name-fuel\">extreme storms</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个异常的蛋。与奇异的深空“生物”相遇后，它的古怪音乐变得更加活跃和不安。<br><br>被触摸时，它会生成一个被<span class=\"name name-fuel\">极端风暴</span>笼罩的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">尘埃世界</span>的强大幻象。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一顆異常的蛋。自從遭遇詭異外太空「生物」之後，蛋裡頭傳出的奇怪音樂越來越活躍和躁動。<br><br>觸摸時會出現強大幻象，讓人看到因<span class=\"name name-fuel\">極端風暴</span>肆虐而<span class=\"name name-stellar\">塵土飛楊的世界</span>。"
  },
